# Cloudflare Pages redirects.
#
# IMPORTANT: do NOT add `/  /en  301` here. The SPA is served at the root `/`,
# and an existing edge rule already redirects /en, /vi, /pip-view -> / (308).
# A `/ -> /en` rule collides with that and creates an infinite 301<->308 loop.
#
# Real files (/assets, /img, /sitemap.xml ...) and the edge-routed locale paths
# are resolved before this rule, so only genuinely-unknown paths fall through.

# Unknown paths -> real 404 (kills soft-404 / index bloat).
/*    /404.html   404
